nodes.text: Pinurquians were a species of horned humanoids active in the galaxy. One well known member was Tinketh Fo, the leader of the planet Keyorin.

The Alderaanian Resistance encountered the animated corpse of a Pinurquian in Darth Rivan's secret archive room on Almas. The Pinurquian had been killed in a firefight between the Stalfonauts and Jacen Yar's team of bounty hunters.
